# Email Classification and PII Masking System

This project implements an email classification system with PII masking for a company's support team.

## Features

- Detection and masking of PII (Personal Identifiable Information)
- Email classification into support categories
- REST API for integration with other systems

## Setup

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/jenniferteresageorge/email-classification.git
   cd email-classification